HEADWORD: Self-confident
<hw>Self`-con"fi*dent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Confident of
one's own strength or powers; relying on one's judgment or ability;
self-reliant.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Self`-con"fi*dent*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

